    "Privacy of data and information was identified as a major concern of organisations by some of the participants in a few studies including [G6], [G27].",
    "A participant in [G6] said: ɓ \"And one of the first questions is privacy; that is, these algorithms that you are presenting, where are they going to be run?",
    "What will their information requirements be?",
    "\"-AI practitioner- [G6].",
    "Few AI practitioners who participated in a study [G6] also seemed to be aware of the gap that exists between ethical principles and the practice of implementing AI ethics."
